title: 15: How To Create New Habits Fast with Dr. Fogg
description:
In this episode, habits expert Dr. BJ Fogg and I go in-depth on the steps you can take to create a new, powerful habit. We are our habits, so this episode is crucial to developing the positive change you desire.
